snippet: Gov. Williams has just transmitted his annual message to the Legislature. He expresses his thanks to the people for their confidence, and proposes to cooperate with the Legislature in whatever is for the public good....
lead_paragraph: Gov. Williams has just transmitted his annual message to the Legislature. He expresses his thanks to the people for their confidence, and proposes to cooperate with the Legislature in whatever is for the public good.

headline.main: Message of the Governor of Vermont.
